title: BRIEF-BOCOM International Holdings Says To Subscribe For Limited Partnership Interest In Easter Capital Fund L.P.

Feb 20 (Reuters) - BOCOM International Holdings Co Ltd :
* CO TO SUBSCRIBE FOR LIMITED PARTNERSHIP INTEREST IN EASTER CAPITAL FUND L.P. WITH CAPITAL COMMITMENT OF US$15.6 MILLION
* ON 15 FEB 2018, UNIT SUBSCRIBED FOR LTD PARTNERSHIP INTEREST IN HHJL CO-INVEST II L.P. , CAPITAL COMMITMENT OF US$36.1 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
